```python
def prob_in_group(groups, data, target, task, summary=False, 
    methods=['F_Statistics', 'Mutual_Information', 'Regularization', 'ReliefF', 'MRMR']) :
    
    if summary==True:
        print('# Probability In Group #')
    
    if type(d) is dict :
        groups = groups.values()
    df_train, df_test = train_test_split(data, test_size=0.2, random_state=1) # X&y_Train, X&y_test DataFrame 
    index_ = methods + ['Prob_{}'.format(mtd) for mtd in methods]
    if task == 'reg':
        select1 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=f_regression)
        select2 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=partial(mutual_info_regression, random_state=1))
        select3 = ElasticNet(random_state=1)
        select5 = 'mrmr_regression(X=X_df, y=y_df, K=0, return_scores=True, show_progress=False)'
    elif task == 'clf' :
        select1 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=f_classif)
        select2 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=partial(mutual_info_classification, random_state=1))
        select3 = LogisticRegression(solver='saga', max_iter=len(X), penalty='elasticnet', l1_ratio=0.5, random_state=1)
        select5 = 'mrmr_classif(X=X_df, y=y_df, K=0, return_scores=True, show_progress=False)'
    select4 = ReliefF()
    text1, text2, text3, text4 = \
    '## F-test Method ##', '## Mutual Information Method ##', '## Regularization Method ##', '## ReliefF Method ##'
    attr1, attr2, attr3, attr4  = 'scores_', 'scores_', 'coef_', 'feature_importances_'
    
    methods_ = [mtd for mtd in methods if mtd != 'MRMR']
    method_idx = [['F_Statistics','Mutual_Information','Regularization', 'ReliefF'].index(i) for i in methods_]   
    lst1, lst2, lst3 = [select1, select2, select3, select4], [text1, text2, text3, text4], [attr1, attr2, attr3, attr4]
    lst1, lst2, lst3 = [lst1[idx] for idx in method_idx], [lst2[idx] for idx in method_idx], [lst3[idx] for idx in method_idx] 

    result_prob_in_group = {}    
    for i, group in tqdm(enumerate(groups, start=1)): 
        X_df, y_df = df_train[group], df_train[target] # pd.DataFrame : MRMR 실행 조건 
        X, y = np.array(X_df), np.array(y_df) # array : ReliefF 실행 조건
        scores, scores_prob = [], []
        for (select_, text_, attr_) in zip(lst1, lst2, lst3):
            select = select_
            select.fit(X, y)
            score = eval('select.{}'.format(attr_))
            # 음수 score처리
            if select == select3 : # ElasticNet(random_state=1) :
                select.fit(MinMaxScaler().fit_transform(X), y)
                score = abs(select.coef_)
            else : 
                score = [0 if s<0 else s for s in score]
            # prob 형태 변환
            if len(group) == 1 :
                score_prob = [1] 
            elif sum(score) == 0 :
                score_prob = [0] * len(group) 
            else : 
                score_prob = list((score / sum(score))) # list : ReliefF 실행에 필요
            scores.append(score) 
            scores_prob.append(score_prob)    
        if 'MRMR' in methods : # 모듈 형태라서 별도로 처리
            score = list(eval(select5)[1].values)
            if len(group) == 1 :
                score_prob = [1] 
            elif sum(score) == 0 :
                score_prob = [0] * len(group) 
            else : 
                score_prob = list((score / sum(score))) 
            scores.append(score) 
            scores_prob.append(score_prob)
            
        df_score = pd.DataFrame(scores + scores_prob, index=index_, columns=group).\
                    rename_axis('Method').rename_axis('Features', axis=1).T
        df_score.loc['Sum', index_[len(methods)]:] = df_score.loc[:, index_[len(methods)]:].sum().values
        df_score['Prob_mean'] = df_score.iloc[:, -len(methods):].mean(axis=1)
        result_prob_in_group['Group{}'.format(i)] = df_score['Prob_mean'][:-1].values   
        
        if summary==True :
            display(df_score.fillna('').style.set_caption('Group{} Selection Score & Probability'.format(i)).\
                                  applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : yellow', subset=(slice(None), 'Prob_mean')))   
    if summary==True:
        print('\n\n')
        
    return result_prob_in_group

def feature_selection(groups, data, target, task, metric=None, summary=False, 
                      methods=['F_statistics','Mutual_Information','ReliefF','Regularization','MRMR'], 
                      models=['DT','RF','GB','LGBM','XGB'], importances=['F_I','P_I']) :

    start = time.time()  
    result_prob_in_group = prob_in_group(groups, data, target, task, summary=summary, 
                                         methods=methods)
    print("time :", time.time() - start) 
    
    start = time.time()  
    result_representative = representative_in_group(groups, data, target, task, summary=summary, 
                                                    models=models, importances=importances) 
    print("time :", time.time() - start) 
    
    start = time.time()  
    result_prob_inter_group = prob_inter_group(result_representative, data, target, task, summary=summary, 
                                                models=models, importances=importances) 
    print("time :", time.time() - start) 
    
    prob = result_prob_in_group.copy()
    prob['Groups'] = result_prob_inter_group
    
    return prob
```

```python
    abs_prob = []
    for i in range(len(abs_) ):
        if abs_.sum(axis=1)[i] == 0 :
            abs_prob.append([0]*len(abs_[i]))
        else : 
            abs_prob.append(abs_[i]/abs_.sum(axis=1)[i])
        print(abs_prob[-1])
    print()
    sum_abs_prob =  np.sum(abs_prob, axis=0)
    print(sum_abs_prob, '\n')
    print(sum_abs_prob/sum(sum_abs_prob), '\n\n')
```

```python
    index_ = methods + ['Prob_{}'.format(mtd) for mtd in methods]
    if task == 'reg':
        select1 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=f_regression)
        select2 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=partial(mutual_info_regression, random_state=1))
        select3 = ElasticNet(random_state=1)
        select5 = 'mrmr_regression(X=X_df, y=y_df, K=0, return_scores=True, show_progress=False)'
    elif task == 'clf' :
        select1 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=f_classif)
        select2 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=partial(mutual_info_classification, random_state=1))
        select3 = LogisticRegression(solver='saga', max_iter=len(X), penalty='elasticnet', l1_ratio=0.5, random_state=1)
        select5 = 'mrmr_classif(X=X_df, y=y_df, K=0, return_scores=True, show_progress=False)'
    select4 = ReliefF()
    text1, text2, text3, text4 = \
    '## F-test Method ##', '## Mutual Information Method ##', '## Regularization Method ##', '## ReliefF Method ##'
    attr1, attr2, attr3, attr4  = 'scores_', 'scores_', 'coef_', 'feature_importances_'
    
    methods_ = [mtd for mtd in methods if mtd != 'MRMR']
    method_idx = [['F_Statistics','Mutual_Information','Regularization', 'ReliefF'].index(i) for i in methods_]   
    lst1, lst2, lst3 = [select1, select2, select3, select4], [text1, text2, text3, text4], [attr1, attr2, attr3, attr4]
    lst1, lst2, lst3 = [lst1[idx] for idx in method_idx], [lst2[idx] for idx in method_idx], [lst3[idx] for idx in method_idx] 

    result_prob_in_group = {}    
    for i, group in enumerate(groups, start=1): 
        X_df, y_df = df_train[group], df_train[target] # pd.DataFrame : MRMR 실행 조건 
        X, y = np.array(X_df), np.array(y_df) # array : ReliefF 실행 조건
        scores, scores_prob = [], []
        for (select_, text_, attr_) in zip(lst1, lst2, lst3):
            select = select_
            select.fit(X, y)
            score = eval('select.{}'.format(attr_))
            # 음수 score처리
            if select == select3 : # ElasticNet(random_state=1) :
                select.fit(MinMaxScaler().fit_transform(X), y)
                score = abs(select.coef_)
            else : 
                score = [0 if s<0 else s for s in score]
            # prob 형태 변환
            if len(group) == 1 :
                score_prob = [1] 
            elif sum(score) == 0 :
                score_prob = [0] * len(group) 
            else : 
                score_prob = list((score / sum(score))) # list : ReliefF 실행에 필요
            scores.append(score) 
            scores_prob.append(score_prob)    
        if 'MRMR' in methods : # 모듈 형태라서 별도로 처리
            score = list(eval(select5)[1].values)
            if len(group) == 1 :
                score_prob = [1] 
            elif sum(score) == 0 :
                score_prob = [0] * len(group) 
            else : 
                score_prob = list((score / sum(score))) 
            scores.append(score) 
            scores_prob.append(score_prob)
            
        df_score = pd.DataFrame(scores + scores_prob, index=index_, columns=group).\
                    rename_axis('Method').rename_axis('Features', axis=1).T
        df_score.loc['Sum', index_[len(methods)]:] = df_score.loc[:, index_[len(methods)]:].sum().values
        df_score['Prob_mean'] = df_score.iloc[:, -len(methods):].mean(axis=1)
        result_prob_in_group['Group{}'.format(i)] = df_score['Prob_mean'][:-1].values   
        
        if summary==True :
            display(df_score.fillna('').style.set_caption('Group{} Selection Score & Probability'.format(i)).\
                                  applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : yellow', subset=(slice(None), 'Prob_mean')))   
    if summary==True:
        print('\n\n')
        
    return result_prob_in_group
    
result_prob_in_group = prob_in_group(groups, data, 'body_mass_g', 'reg', summary=True, methods=['Regularization', 'ReliefF', 'MRMR'])
```

```python
    if metric is not None :
        metric_ = metric
    models_index = [['DT','RF','GB','LGBM','XGB'].index(i) for i in models]
    models_ = [models_[idx] for idx in models_index]

    result_representative = []
    for i, group in enumerate(groups, start=1):     
        df_importance = pd.DataFrame([])
        for i, model in enumerate(models_, start=1) :
            X, y = df_train[group], df_train[target] 
            str_ = ''.join([i for i in type(model).__name__ if i.isupper()])
            if len(group) > 1 :
                model.fit(X, y) 
                if 'F_I' in importances :
                    f_i = model.feature_importances_ 
                    df_importance['Prob_F_I_{}'.format(str_)] = f_i / sum(f_i) # lgbm만 sum=1 형태가 아님
                if 'P_I' in importances :
                    p_i = permutation_importance(model,X,y,random_state=1,scoring=metric)['importances_mean']
                    p_i = [0 if i<0 else i for i in p_i] # 음수는 0으로 두고 확률값 만듬
                    df_importance['Prob_P_I_{}'.format(str_)] = p_i / sum(p_i) 
            else : # 변수 1개면 model fit 안 됨
                df_importance.loc[0, ['Prob_{}_{}'.format(imp, str_) for imp in importances]] = [1]*len(importances)
                
        df_importance.index = group
        df_importance['Prob_mean'] = df_importance.mean(axis=1) / sum(df_importance.mean(axis=1)) # 각 기법의 평균들로 확률값 만듬
        df_importance.loc['sum'] = df_importance.sum()
        df_importance = df_importance.rename_axis('Method', axis=1).rename_axis('Features')
        representative = df_importance.index[df_importance['Prob_mean'][:-1].argmax()]
        result_representative.append(representative)
        
        if summary==True:
            if 'P_I' in importances :
                str_ = ' & '.join(importances).format(metric_).\
                        replace('F_I','Feature Importance').replace('P_I','Permutation Importance')
            else : 
                str_ = ' & '.join(importances).replace('F_I','Feature Importance').replace('P_I','Permutation Importance')
            display(df_importance.style.set_caption(str_).\
                                  applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : red', subset=(representative, 'Prob_mean')))
    if summary==True:
        print('\n\n\n')

    return result_representative

result_representative = representative_in_group(groups, data, 'body_mass_g', 'reg', summary=True, 
                        models=['DT','RF', 'LGBM','XGB'], importances=['P_I'])
```

```python
def prob_inter_group(representatives, data, target, task, metric=None, summary=False, 
                    models=['DT','RF','GB','LGBM','XGB'], 
                    importances=['F_I','P_I']): 
    if summary==True:
        print('# Probability inter Group #')
    
    df_train, df_test = train_test_split(data, test_size=0.2, random_state=1) # X&y_Train, X&y_test DataFrame 
    if task == 'reg':
        metric_ = 'neg_mean_squared_error' # arg : 'r2'
        models_ = [DecisionTreeRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMRegressor(random_state=1, importance_type='gain'), 
                  XGBRegressor(random_state=1, importance_type='gain')]
    elif task == 'clf' :
        metric_ = 'accuracy' # arg : 'f1', 'f1_macro'
        models_ = [DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMClassifier(random_state=1, importance_type='gain'), 
                  XGBClassifier(random_state=1, importance_type='gain')]   
    if metric is not None :
        metric_ = metric
    models_index = [['DT','RF','GB','LGBM','XGB'].index(i) for i in models]
    models_ = [models_[idx] for idx in models_index]

    df_importance = pd.DataFrame([])
    for i, model in enumerate(models_, start=1) :
        X, y = df_train[representatives], df_train[target] 
        str_ = ''.join([i for i in type(model).__name__ if i.isupper()])
        if len(representatives) > 1 :
            model.fit(X, y) 
            if 'F_I' in importances :
                f_i = model.feature_importances_ 
                df_importance['Prob_F_I_{}'.format(str_)] = f_i / sum(f_i) # lgbm만 sum=1 형태가 아님
            if 'P_I' in importances :
                p_i = permutation_importance(model,X,y,random_state=1,scoring=metric)['importances_mean']
                p_i = [0 if i<0 else i for i in p_i] # 음수는 0으로 두고 확률값 만듬
                df_importance['Prob_P_I_{}'.format(str_)] = p_i / sum(p_i)            
        else : # 변수 1개면 model fit 안 됨
            df_importance.loc[0, ['Prob_{}_{}'.format(imp, str_) for imp in importances]] = [1]*len(importances)

    df_importance.index = representatives
    df_importance['Prob_mean'] = df_importance.mean(axis=1) / sum(df_importance.mean(axis=1)) # 각 기법의 평균들로 확률값 만듬
    df_importance.loc['sum'] = df_importance.sum()
    df_importance = df_importance.rename_axis('Method', axis=1).rename_axis('Features')
    result_prob_inter_group = df_importance['Prob_mean'][:-1].values
    
    if summary==True:
        if 'P_I' in importances :
            str_ = ' & '.join(importances).format(metric_).\
                    replace('F_I','Feature Importance').replace('P_I','Permutation Importance')
        else : 
            str_ = ' & '.join(importances).replace('F_I','Feature Importance').replace('P_I','Permutation Importance')
        display(df_importance.style.set_caption(str_).\
                                  applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : yellow', subset=(slice(None), 'Prob_mean')))

    return result_prob_inter_group

result_prob_inter_group = prob_inter_group(result_representative, data, 'body_mass_g', 'reg', summary=True, 
                        models=['DT','RF', 'LGBM','XGB'], importances=['P_I'])
```

```python
def feature_selection(groups, data, target, task, metric=None, summary=False, 
                      methods=['F_statistics','Mutual_Information','ReliefF'], 
                      models=['DT','RF','GB','LGBM','XGB'], importances=['F_I','P_I']) :

    result_prob_in_group = prob_in_group(groups, data, target, task, summary=summary, 
                                         methods=methods)
    result_representative = representative_in_group(groups, data, target, task, summary=summary, 
                                                    models=models, importances=importances) 
    result_prob_inter_group = prob_inter_group(result_representative, data, target, task, summary=summary, 
                                                models=models, importances=importances) 
    
    prob = result_prob_in_group.copy()
    prob['Groups'] = result_prob_inter_group
    return prob
    
prob = feature_selection(groups, data, 'body_mass_g', 'reg', metric=None, summary=True, 
                                  methods=['F_statistics','Mutual_Information','ReliefF'], 
                                  models=['DT','RF','GB','LGBM'], importances=['F_I','P_I'])
```

```python
# selections

# score_in_pool
# 전체 selection method에 대해 selected_rate로 상위 n %를 선별
# -> importance외의 기법들의 수치들을 통합해서 지수를 부여해서 합이1이되도록 확률값으로 변환
    # 1) 각 기법의 점수를 받아서 정규화하고, 합산을 한 후 확률(가중합1)로 변환하기.
        # 기법별 score들을 정규화 (ex. corr=[0.1, 0.3, 0.5] -> [0, 0.5, 1])
        # 기법별 정규화한 값을 합산 (corr=[0, 0.5, 1], m.i=[0, 0.7, 1] =>  합=[0, 1.2, ,2]) 
        # 합산한 값을 합이 1이 되도록 만든 값이 그룹 내 확률 [0, 1.2, 2] -> [0, 1.2/3.2, 2/3.2]
        # score = score1_scaled + score2_scaled + score3_scaled
        # score_p = score / score.sum()   
    # 2) 각 기법의 점수를 받아서 정규화하고, 확률(가중합1)로 변환해서, 1/n배 곱해서 더하기
        # score1_scaled = MinMaxScaler().fit_transform(score1.reshape(-1,1)).reshape(-1)
        # score2_scaled = MinMaxScaler().fit_transform(score2.reshape(-1,1)).reshape(-1)
        # score3_scaled = MinMaxScaler().fit_transform(score3.reshape(-1,1)).reshape(-1)
        # score1_scaled_p = score1_scaled / score1_scaled.sum()
        # score2_scaled_p = score2_scaled / score2_scaled.sum()
        # score3_scaled_p = score3_scaled / score3_scaled.sum()
        # score_p = mean(score1_scaled_p+score2_scaled_p+score3_scaled_p)
    # 3) 각 기법의 점수를 빈도(확률로) 변환하고, 1/n배 곱해서 더하기. 
        # 주의 : statistic 최소가 0이 아니고 음수가 나올 수 있는 기법
    
    # 3 선택
    # 정규화 : 비중고려 x, 서열 간격 고려
    # 확률화 : 비중고려 O, 서열 간격 고려
    
# impotance_inter_pool
# 변수가 줄어들 때마다의 importance 비교가 어려워 RFE 방식 뺌
    # 연산량 : 대표변수개수 * 모델개수 
    # [a,b,c,d] [0,1,0.2,0.2,0.5] -> # [b,c,d] [0,2,0.3,0.5] -> # [c,d][0.3, 0.7] 
    # [a,b,c,d] [0,1, 0.2, 0.8/3, 1.7/3] => [0.1, 0.2 0.266, 0.566] => sum1

# feature importance : high cardinality 문제 + gain, split 방식 통일 필요
# permutation importace를 구하고 (gain split 방식이 따로 있는지??)
    # sum1(확률) 형태로 바꾸고 1/n배 곱함
    
def selections(data, target, task, methods=['F_statistics','Mutual_Information','ReliefF']):
    X, y = data.drop([target], axis=1), data[target]
    X, y = np.array(X), np.array(y)

    if task == 'reg':
        select1 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=f_regression)
        select2 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=partial(mutual_info_regression, random_state=1))
    elif task == 'clf' :
        select1 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=f_regression)
        select2 = SelectPercentile(percentile=100, score_func=partial(mutual_info_regression, random_state=1))
    select3 = skrebate.ReliefF()
    text1, text2, text3 = '## F-test method ##', '## Mutual Information method ##', '## ReliefF method ##'
           
    lst1_, lst2_, lst3_ = [select1, select2, select3], [text1, text2, text3], ['scores_', 'scores_', 'feature_importances_']
    scores, method_idx = [], [['F_statistics','Mutual_Information','ReliefF'].index(i) for i in methods]
    for i, lst in enumerate([lst1_, lst2_, lst3_], start=1) :  
         globals()['lst{}'.format(i)] = [lst[idx] for idx in method_idx] # in 안에서 참조하고 있어서 할당이 적용 안 되는듯?
    for (select_, text_, score_) in zip(lst1, lst2, lst3):
        select = select_
        select.fit(X,y)
        score = eval('select.{}'.format(score_))
        score = [0 if s<0 else s for s in score] # relief 음수 가능
        scores.append(score) 
        # print(text_, '\n', select, '\n score : \n', score.round(3), '\n')  
    
    return scores # selection method 별 score
```

```python
def prob_in_group(groups, data, target, task, metric=None, summary=False, methods=['F_statistics','Mutual_Information','ReliefF'],
                    models=['DT','RF','XGB','LGBM','XGB'], importances=['F_I','P_I']): # group 내 변수별 확률 및 대표 선수 선별 #
    
    global result_top1
    result_score, result_top1 = {}, [] 
    methods_ = methods
    
    if task == 'reg':
        index_ = methods_ + ['Prob_{}'.format(mtd) for mtd in methods_] + ['Prob_in_Group']
        metric_ = 'neg_mean_squared_error' # arg : 'r2'
        models_ = [DecisionTreeRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMRegressor(random_state=1, importance_type='gain'), 
                  XGBRegressor(random_state=1, importance_type='gain')]
    elif task == 'clf' :
        index_ = methods_ + ['Prob_{}'.format(mtd) for mtd in methods_] + ['Prob_in_Group']
        metric_ = 'accuracy' # arg : 'f1', 'f1_macro'
        models_ = [DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMClassifier(random_state=1, importance_type='gain'), 
                  XGBClassifier(random_state=1, importance_type='gain')]   
    if metric is not None :
        metric_ = metric
    models_index = [models.index(i) for i in ['DT','RF','XGB','LGBM']]
    models_ = [models_[idx] for idx in models_index]

    for i, group in enumerate(groups, start=1): 
        df = data[group + [target]] 
        df, test = train_test_split(df, test_size=0.2, random_state=1) # X&y DataFrame 형태 
        scores, scores_lst, scores_p_lst = selections(df, target, task, methods=methods_), [], []
        for j in range(len(scores)):
            scores_lst.append(scores[j])
            if len(group) != 1:
                scores_p_lst.append(scores[j] / np.float64(sum(scores[j]))) # list/int,float: Err 
            else :
                scores_p_lst.append((np.array([1])))    
        score = sum(scores_p_lst) / len(scores)
        display(type(scores_lst), type(scores_p_lst), type(scores_lst), type(scores_p_lst)) ###
        display(scores_lst, scores_p_lst, scores_lst+scores_p_lst) ###
        df_score = pd.DataFrame(scores_lst + scores_p_lst + [score], columns=group, index=index_).\
                    rename_axis('Method').rename_axis('Features', axis=1).T
        df_score.loc['sum', index_[len(methods_)]:] = df_score.loc[:, index_[len(methods_)]:].sum().values
        
#         score1, score2, score3 = selections(df, target, task, methods)
#         score1_p, score2_p, score3_p = score1/score1.sum(), score2/score2.sum(), score3/score3.sum()
#         score = (score1_p+score2_p+score3_p)/3        
#         df_score = pd.DataFrame([score1, score2, score3, score1_p, score2_p, score3_p, score], columns=group, 
#                         index=index_).rename_axis('Method').rename_axis('Features', axis=1).T
#         df_score.loc['sum', 'prob_1':] = df_score.loc[:, 'prob_1':].sum().values
        
        if summary==True :
            display(df_score.fillna('').style.set_caption('Group{} Score & Probability'.format(i)).\
                                  applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : yellow', subset=(slice(None), 'Prob_in_Group')))
        result_score['Group{}'.format(i)]=(score)
    
        df_importance = pd.DataFrame([])
        for i, model in enumerate(models_, start=1) :
            X, y = df.drop([target], axis=1), df[target]
            model_ = model 
            str_ = ''.join([i for i in type(model_).__name__ if i.isupper()])
            if len(group) > 1 :
                model_.fit(X, y) 
                if 'F_I' in importances :
                    f_i = model_.feature_importances_ 
                    df_importance['F_I_{}'.format(str_)] = f_i / sum(f_i) # lgbm만 sum=1 형태가 아님
                if 'P_I' in importances :
                    p_i = permutation_importance(model_,X,y,random_state=1,scoring=metric)['importances_mean']
                    p_i = [0 if i<0 else i for i in p_i] # 음수는 0으로 두고 확률값 만듬
                    df_importance['P_I_{}'.format(str_)] = p_i / sum(p_i)            
            else : # 변수 1개면 model fit 안 됨
                df_importance.loc[0, ['{}_{}'.format(imp, str_) for imp in importances]] = [1]*len(importances)
                
        df_importance.index = group
        df_importance['mean'] = df_importance.mean(axis=1) / sum(df_importance.mean(axis=1)) # 각 기법의 평균들로 확률값 만듬
        df_importance.loc['sum'] = df_importance.sum()
        df_importance = df_importance.rename_axis('Method', axis=1).rename_axis('Features')
        top1 = df_importance.index[df_importance['mean'][:-1].argmax()]
        result_top1.append(top1)
        if summary==True:
            display(df_importance.style.set_caption('Permutation Importance ({}) : each method sum to 1'.format(metric_)).\
                                  applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : red', subset=(top1, 'mean')))
            print()

    print('\n# return : Group 내 확률 #')
    display(result_score)
    return result_score


start = time.time()  
score = prob_in_group(groups, data, 'body_mass_g', 'reg', summary=True, methods=['F_statistics', 'ReliefF'],
                   models=['DT','RF','XGB','LGBM'], importances=['F_I'])
print("time :", time.time() - start)
```

```python
def prob_inter_group(data, target, task, metric=None, summary=False, 
                     models=['DT','RF','XGB','LGBM','XGB'], importances=['F','P']):   
    cols = result_top1
    df = data[cols + [target]]
    df, test = train_test_split(df, test_size=0.2, random_state=1) # X&y DataFrame 형태 
    # If you don’t have a separate held-out dataset, you can fit PermutationImportance on the same data as used for training; 
    # this still allows to inspect the model, but doesn’t show which features are important for generalization.
    X, y = df.drop([target], axis=1), df[target]
   
    
    # Model Based (Wrapper, Embedded) #
    if task == 'reg':
        metric_ = 'neg_mean_squared_error' # arg : 'r2'
        models_ = [DecisionTreeRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMRegressor(random_state=1, importance_type='gain'), 
                  XGBRegressor(random_state=1, importance_type='gain')]
    elif task == 'clf' :
        metric_ = 'accuracy' # arg : 'f1', 'f1_macro'
        models_ = [DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMClassifier(random_state=1, importance_type='gain'), 
                  XGBClassifier(random_state=1, importance_type='gain')]
    if metric is not None :
        metric_ = metric
    models_index = [models.index(i) for i in ['DT','RF','XGB','LGBM']]
    models_ = [models_[idx] for idx in models_index]

    
    ## Selection Using Model ##
    if summary == True :
        print('# Model Based Importance Method #')
        display(models_)
    df_importance = pd.DataFrame([])
    for i, model in enumerate(models_, start=1):
        model_ = model 
        model_.fit(X, y) 
        str_ = ''.join([i for i in type(model_).__name__ if i.isupper()])
        
        if 'F_I' in importances :
            f_i = model_.feature_importances_
            df_importance['F_I_{}'.format(str_)] = f_i / sum(f_i) # lgbm만 sum=1 형태가 아님
        if 'P_I' in importances :
            p_i = permutation_importance(model_,X,y,random_state=1,scoring=metric)['importances_mean']
            p_i = [0 if i<0 else i for i in p_i] # 음수는 0으로 두고 확률값 만듬
            df_importance['P_I_{}'.format(str_)] = p_i / sum(p_i)
            
    df_importance['mean'] = df_importance.mean(axis=1) / sum(df_importance.mean(axis=1)) # 각 기법의 평균들로 확률값 만듬
    df_importance.index = (cols)
    df_importance.loc['sum'] = df_importance.sum()
    df_importance = df_importance.rename_axis('Method', axis=1).rename_axis('그룹별 대표 Features')
    if summary == True :
        display(df_importance.style.set_caption('Feature Importance & Permutation Importance ({}) : each method sum to 1'.format(metric_)).\
                                applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : yellow', subset='mean'))
    
    print('\n# return : Group 별 확률 #')
    print(df_importance['mean'][:-1].values)
    return df_importance['mean'][:-1].values
```

```python
Feature Selection Pseudo-Code

0. 활용 어려운 변수 처리 + 유사 변수 그룹핑

1. 변수 그룹 A(A0,A1,A2,...), B(B0,B1), C(OHE.Categ변수. C0, C1, C2) ... 을 input으로 받음

2. 각 그룹별로 selection 기법을 적용하여, 그룹별 후보 변수 선별 과정
    2-1. 개별 기법들에 대하여 기준 설정 (상위n% 선택 or threshold)
         ex. corr 0.7 이상, Featrue Importance 상위 50% 등..
         * Categ변수에 적용하는 기법은 별도
    2-2. 여러가지 기법 기준 결과로 voting 하여 ranking 산출. 
         상위 n%를 그룹별 후보 변수로 선정.
         ex. A그룹 ranking : [A0, A1, A2, A3] => [A0, A1] (50%)
    2-3. 원본 변수는 항상 선별 

3. 후보 변수 전체에 대해 selection 기법을 적용하여, 각 후보 그룹의 class(always, useful, normal, useless) 구분 과정
    3-1. 2-1,2-2를 반복하여 ranking 산출
         ranking 결과로 그룹별 top1 변수 선별.
    3-2. 그룹별 top1 변수의 ranking 기준으로 그룹의 class 구분 
         1) ranking 상위 5%는 always, 5~50은 useful... (?)
         2) 전체 기법 중 90%이상 선택 always, 50~90% 이상 선택 useful (?)
         
    
    3-1. 특정 selection 기법(ex. F.E) 적용
         해당 기법의 설명력을 기준으로 ranking. 
    3-2. 그룹별 top1 변수의 설명력을 기준으로 그룹의 class 구분 
         1) ranking 상위 5%는 always, 5~50은 useful... (?)
         2) F.E n0 이상은 always, n1~n2은 useful... (?)
    
    * 차이 : 여러 기법의 voting결과 ranking으로 서열 / 단일 기법의 척도(설명력) ranking으로 서열
    * 가지고 있는 것 중에서는 가장 중요한 것이 맞는 시각이라면 ranking으로 짤라도 무방?
    * class 구분 backdata
        
    3-3. class별 선택 규칙 적용해 변수 선택 (output)
        always : top1 선택. 
        useful : 후보 중 택1
        normal : 후보 중 택1 or 미선택 
        useless : 미선택
        
4. 총 경우의 수 산출 & total feature 개수를 N개 under로 제어
    4-1. 총 경우의 수 = (각 uselful 그룹별 변수 종류 수) * (각 normal 그룹별 변수 종류 수 +1) 
    4-2. 총 경우의 수가 N 초과할 경우, 2-2의 상위 n 조정하면서 과정 반복.
```

```python
def feature_selection_all(data, target, task,

                          method3 = RFE(estimator=DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), n_features_to_select=1),
                          # method3 = RFECV(estimator=DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), cv=3, scoring='accuracy', n_jobs=-1),
                          method4 = SelectFromModel(estimator=DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), threshold='1.25*mean')
                          ): ## 개별 selection에서의 pick을 반영하고 싶으면 : 비중 percentile50 등을 인자로 넣을 수있게 
    
    global X, y, cols, select, lst_select, num_method, rank1, rank2, rank3_1, rank3_2, rank4_1, rank4_2 # 뒤의 함수에서도 사용
    X,y = data.drop([target], axis=1), data[target]
    cols = X.columns
    lst_select = []
             
    # Univariate feature selection. 일변량 방법 : SelectPercentile, SelectKBest #
    print('\n\n # F-test method #')
    if task == 'reg':
        arg = f_regression # mutual_info_classif, r2
    else :
        arg = f_classif # mutual_info_regression, chi2   
    param = method2.get_params(deep=False) 
    param['score_func'] = arg  # **(가변인자) 활용한 변경 예시: param = {**method2.get_params(deep=False), **{'arg1':a, 'arg2':'b}}  
    method2 = SelectPercentile(**param)  
    feature_selection(method2)
    ## print('p_val :', '\n',  select.pvalues_)
    ## print('f_stats :', '\n',  select.scores_)   
    rank2 = list(pd.Series(select.scores_).rank(ascending=False).astype(int))  

    ## Model Based (Wrapper, Embedded) ##
    if task == 'reg':
        models = [DecisionTreeRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMRegressor(random_state=1), 
                  XGBRegressor(random_state=1)]
    else : 
        models = [DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  RandomForestClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  LGBMClassifier(random_state=1), 
                  XGBClassifier(random_state=1)]
    models = models[:2] ###
    
    # RFECV
    # print('\n\n\n # RFECV method')
    # if task == 'reg':
    #     arg = 'r2'

    #    param = method3.get_params(deep=False)

    #    method3 = RFECV(**param) 
    #    feature_selection(method3)
    #    print("Feature Ranking: %s" % select.ranking_, '\n')
    #    plot_cv(select)    
    
    # RFE
    print('\n\n # RFE method #') 
    for i, model in enumerate(models, start=1) :
        print('Model :', model)
        method3 = RFE(estimator=model, n_features_to_select=1)  
        feature_selection(method3) 
        globals()['rank3_{}'.format(i)] = list(pd.Series(select.ranking_).rank(ascending=True).astype(int))  
        
    # Selection Using Model
    print('\n\n  # Model Selection method #')
    for i, model in enumerate(models, start=1) :
        print('Model :', model)
        param = method4.get_params(deep=False) 
        param['estimator'] = model
        method4 = SelectFromModel(**param)  
        feature_selection(method4)
        
        model_ = model # SelectFromModel 내에 F.E 제공하는 attribute가 없어 대체
        model_.fit(X, y) 
        print('importance : \n', model_.feature_importances_, '\n') 
        globals()['rank4_{}'.format(i)] = list(pd.Series(model_.feature_importances_).rank(ascending=False).astype(int)) 

    # Pool selection 
    print('\n\n # Selection 별 순위 및 선택여부')
    num_method = 5
    df_voting = pd.Series(np.zeros((len(cols))).astype(int), index=cols).to_frame(name='selected_num')
    for selected_feature in np.hstack(lst_select):
        df_voting.loc[selected_feature, 'selected_num'] += 1
    df_voting['selected_rate'] = (df_voting['selected_num'] / num_method *100).round(2)
 
    return df_voting # dataframe. index=변수, col=선택횟수,비율
```

```python
            plt.figure(figsize=(num_method, len(pool)*0.5))
            plt.xticks(rotation=30)
            sb.heatmap(select_matrix, cmap='Blues_r', cbar=False, linewidths=0.1, vmin=num, vmax=num+1, annot=True);
            plt.show() # vmin=선택할개수, vmax=선택할개수+1 => 선택할개수 기준으로 양극단색(0,1)으로 표현 

            # selection 내의 기준 rank를 통해 vote 집계 (selection 내의 선택 결과와 무관)
            df_voting['selected_num'] = select_matrix[select_matrix <= num].notnull().sum(axis=1)
            df_voting['selected_rate'] = (df_voting['selected_num'] / num_method).round(2)
            df_voting['rank_sum'] = select_matrix.sum(axis=1)
            df_voting = df_voting.sort_values(['selected_rate', 'rank_sum'], ascending=[False, True])
            
            # rank_sum 까지 동률인 경우의 예외처리 : 
            # 선택되는 변수들 중 가장 낮은 순위 변수의 selected_num, rank_sum 값 저장
            # 해당값들이 동률인 변수들만 모은 df에서 맨 뒤의 인덱스(=변수명) 저장, 해당 인덱스까지 선택
            m1,m2 = df_voting.iloc[:num].iloc[-1]['selected_num'], df_voting.iloc[:num].iloc[-1]['rank_sum'] 
            m = df_voting[(df_voting['selected_num']== m1) & (df_voting['rank_sum'] == m2)].index[-1]
            result = df_voting[:m].index.tolist()
            
            len_old = len(result) 
            result += [i for i in pool if '__' not in i] # '__' 유무로 원변수 구분해 pool에 추가   
            result = sorted(list(set(result)), key=list(df_voting.index).index) # 서열유지. key=df_voting.index (X)
            len_new = len(result)
            results.append(result)
            display(df_voting.style.set_caption('Pool{} '.format(i)).\
                            applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : yellow', subset=(result, slice(None))))
            if len_old == len_new :
                print('Pool{} 내 {}개 중 Voting Rank 상위 {}% = {}개 :\n {}'.format(i, len(pool), int(n*100), num, result), '\n'*4) 
            else :
                print('원 변수를 pool에 추가')
                print('Pool{} 내 {}개 중 Voting Rank 상위 {}% + 원변수 = {}개 : \n {}'.\
                      format(i, len(pool), int(n*100), num+len_new-len_old, result), '\n'*4) 

    # 전체 pool 종합
    print('### Pool 내 선별 결과 ###')
    for i, result in enumerate(results, start=1) :
        print('Pool{} : \n {} \n'.format(i,result))
    return results
    
pools_ = selection_in_pool(pools, data, 'body_mass_g', 'reg', n=0.5)
```

```python
def selection_inter_pool(pools, data, target, task, n=0.5, n1=0.75, n2=0.50, n3=0.25, cases=np.Inf):   
    # global cols, df_voting, pool
    cols = list(itertools.chain(*pools))
    df = data[cols + [target]]
    df_voting = feature_selection_all(df, target, task)
    
    pool = df_voting.index 
    num = math.ceil(len(pool)*n) # 선택할 개수
    
    # selection별 변수 순위 및 선택 여부 
    d = dict(method2 = rank2, method3_1 = rank3_1, method3_2 = rank3_2, method4_1 = rank4_1, method4_2 = rank4_2)
    select_matrix = pd.DataFrame({k:pd.Series(v,index=pool) for k,v in d.items()}) 
    plt.figure(figsize=(num_method, len(pool)*0.5))
    plt.xticks(rotation=30)
    sb.heatmap(select_matrix, cmap='Blues_r', cbar=False, linewidths=0.1, vmin=num, vmax=num+1, annot=True);
    plt.show() # vmin=선택할개수, vmax=선택할개수+1 => 선택할개수 기준으로 양극단색(0,1)으로 표현 

    # selection 내의 기준 rank를 통해 vote 집계 (selection 내의 선택 결과와 무관)
    df_voting['selected_num'] = select_matrix[select_matrix <= num].notnull().sum(axis=1)
    df_voting['selected_rate'] = (df_voting['selected_num'] / num_method).round(2)
    df_voting['rank_sum'] = select_matrix.sum(axis=1)
    df_voting = df_voting.sort_values(['selected_rate', 'rank_sum'], ascending=[False, True])
    display(df_voting)

    # rank_sum 까지 동률인 경우의 예외처리 
    # m1,m2 = df_voting.iloc[num_origin-1]['selected_num'], df_voting.iloc[num_origin-1]['rank_sum'] ### slicing이므로 -1
    # m = df_voting[(df_voting['selected_num'] == m1) & (df_voting['rank_sum'] == m2)].index[-1]
    # result = df_voting[:m].index.tolist()
    ## 선택되는 변수들 중 가장 낮은 순위 변수의 selected_num, rank_sum 값 저장
    ## 해당값들이 동률인 변수들만 모은 df에서 맨 뒤의 인덱스(=변수명) 저장, 해당 인덱스까지 선택         
    ###
    
    # pool별 group 부여 : 1위 rank변수의 selected_rate 기준
    order = {} # 정렬된 서열을 각 pool별로 떼어서 볼 때도 유지
    for rank, col in enumerate(list(df_voting.index)):
        order[col] = rank
    
    result, groups, nums = [], [], [], 
    for i, pool in enumerate(pools, start=1):
        pool = sorted(pool, key=lambda x : order[x]) 
        df_ = df_voting.loc[pool]
        
        top, top_, color = df_['selected_rate'].iloc[0], df_['rank_sum'].iloc[0], 'yellow'
        subset_row = [idx for idx in df_.index if (df_.loc[idx,'selected_rate']>n3)]
        if top >= n1 :  ### 동률인경우 처리필요 ###
            features, num_features, group, color, subset_row = [pool[0]], len([pool[0]]), 'Always', 'red', pool[0]
        elif top >= n2 :
            new_pool = df_[df_['selected_rate'] > n3].index.tolist()
            features, num_features, group = new_pool, len(new_pool), 'Useful'
        elif top >= n3 :
            new_pool = df_[df_['selected_rate'] > n3].index.tolist() + [None] 
            features, num_features, group = new_pool, len(new_pool), 'Normal'
        else :
            features, num_features, group = [], 0, 'Useless'
        display(df_.style.set_caption('Pool{} Group : {}'.format(i, group)).\
                        applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : '+color, subset=(subset_row, slice(None))))
        result.append([group,top,top_,num_features,features]) 
        
    # 케이스 수 조정 
    df_result = pd.DataFrame(result, columns=['group', 'top_selected_rate', 'top_rank_sum', 'num_features', 'features'], index=range(1,len(pools)+1)).rename_axis('Pool') 
    df_result = df_result.sort_values(['top_selected_rate', 'top_rank_sum'], ascending=[False, True])
    num_cases = np.prod(df_result[df_result['group'].isin(['Useful', 'Normal'])]['num_features'].values)
    print('\n\n\n\n ### 총 경우의 수 : {} ###'.format(num_cases))
    display(df_result)

    cases_change = False
    while num_cases > cases :
        cases_change = True
        df_result = df_result[:-1]
        num_cases = np.prod(df_result[df_result['group'].isin(['Useful', 'Normal'])]['num_features'].values)
    if cases_change:
        print('\n 설정한 경우의 수 한도 : {} \n 조정된 총 경우의 수 : {}'.format(cases, num_cases))
        display(df_result)
    
    # 결과
    print('\n\n\n\n ### Pool 간 선별 결과 ###')
    for i, r in zip(df_result.sort_index().index, df_result.sort_index()['features']):
        print('Pool{} : \n {} \n'.format(i,r))
    return list(df_result.sort_index()['features'].values)
```

     ### Pool 간 선별 결과 ###
    Pool1 : 
     ['pool1_bill_length_mm__otsu_multi2', 'pool1_bill_length_mm__qcut2', 'pool1_bill_length_mm__grouped_0', 'pool1_bill_length_mm__cut2', 'pool1_bill_length_mm__grouped_1'] 
    
    Pool3 : 
     ['pool3_flipper_length_mm__otsu_multi3', 'pool3_flipper_length_mm__grouped_0', 'pool3_flipper_length_mm__cut3', 'pool3_flipper_length_mm__qcut3'] 
    



```python
# 상대적기준
def selection_inter_pool(pools, data, target, task, n=0.5, num_col=len(pools), cases=np.Inf):   
    cols = list(itertools.chain(*pools))
    df = data[cols + [target]]
    df_voting = feature_selection_all(df, target, task)
    
    pool = df_voting.index 
    num = math.ceil(len(pool)*n) # 선택할 개수
    
    # selection별 변수 순위 및 선택 여부 
    d = dict(method2 = rank2, method3_1 = rank3_1, method3_2 = rank3_2, method4_1 = rank4_1, method4_2 = rank4_2)
    select_matrix = pd.DataFrame({k:pd.Series(v,index=pool) for k,v in d.items()}) 
    plt.figure(figsize=(num_method, len(pool)*0.5))
    plt.xticks(rotation=30)
    sb.heatmap(select_matrix, cmap='Blues_r', cbar=False, linewidths=0.1, vmin=num, vmax=num+1, annot=True);
    plt.show() # vmin=선택할개수, vmax=선택할개수+1 => 선택할개수 기준으로 양극단색(0,1)으로 표현 

    # selection 내의 기준 rank를 통해 vote 집계 (selection 내의 선택 결과와 무관)
    df_voting['selected_num'] = select_matrix[select_matrix <= num].notnull().sum(axis=1)
    df_voting['selected_rate'] = (df_voting['selected_num'] / num_method).round(2)
    df_voting['rank_sum'] = select_matrix.sum(axis=1)
    df_voting = df_voting.sort_values(['selected_rate', 'rank_sum'], ascending=[False, True])
    display(df_voting)

    # pool별 group 부여 : 1위 rank변수의 selected_rate 기준
    order = {} # 정렬된 서열을 각 pool별로 떼어서 볼 때도 유지
    for rank, col in enumerate(list(df_voting.index)):
        order[col] = rank
    result = []
    for i, pool in enumerate(pools, start=1):
        pool = sorted(pool, key=lambda x : order[x]) 
        df_ = df_voting.loc[pool]
        top, top_ = df_['selected_rate'].iloc[0], df_['rank_sum'].iloc[0] ## 동점처리필요 ##
        result.append([top,top_])       
    df_result = pd.DataFrame(result, columns=['top_selected_rate', 'top_rank_sum'], index=range(1,len(pools)+1)).rename_axis('Pool') 
    df_result = df_result.sort_values(['top_selected_rate', 'top_rank_sum'], ascending=[False, True])
    display(df_result)    
    
    ## qcut 대상 : bin 경계 unique가 확보 필요 => index or top_selected_rate의 unique()
    ## cut 대상 : df_result['top_selected_rate'] 
    ### 1. qcut 후 끌어내리기 + 비어 버리면 아래에서 끌어오기
    cut_lst, label = list(range(len(df_result),0,-1)), ['Useless','Normal','Useful','Always']
    df_result['group'] = pd.qcut(cut_lst,4,labels=label)
    for g in reversed(label) :
        try :
            m = df_result[df_result['group'] == g].iloc[-1]['top_selected_rate']
            df_result['group'][df_result['top_selected_rate'] == m] = g
        except :
            pass
    if len(df_result['group'][df_result['group'].isin(['Useful','Normal'])]) == 0: # al,ul -> al,uf
        df_result['group'][df_result['group'] == 'Useless'] = 'Useful'
    if len(df_result['group'][df_result['group'] == 'Useful']) == 0 : # al,n,ul -> al,uf,n
        df_result['group'][df_result['group'] == 'Normal'] = 'Useful'
        df_result['group'][df_result['group'] == 'Useless'] = 'Normal'
    elif len(df_result['group'][df_result['group'] == 'Normal']) == 0 : # al,uf,ul -> al,uf,n  
        df_result['group'][df_result['group'] == 'Useless'] = 'Normal'
    display('1.qcut 후 끌어내리기', df_result)
     
    # 최종 직접 변경
    while True:
        try :
            val,g = input('변경 입력 (ex. 0.5, Useful) :').split()
            df_result['group'][df_result['top_selected_rate'] == val] = g
            display(df_result)
        except : # enter
            break          
            
    # pool 별 group, feature 결과
    top_group = []
    for g in label :
        try :
            top_group.append(df_result[df_result['group'] == g].iloc[0]['top_selected_rate'])
        except:
            top_group.append(0) # 각 group이 항상 생기진 않아 예외처리
        globals()['num_{}'.format(g)] = len(df_result[df_result['group']==g])
    
    result = []
    pools = [pools[i-1] for i in df_result.index] # ∵index=range(1,len(pools)+1) 
    for i_, (i, pool) in zip(df_result.index, enumerate(pools, start=1)):
        pool = sorted(pool, key=lambda x : order[x]) 
        df_, group, top_useless = df_voting.loc[pool], df_result.loc[i_, 'group'], top_group[0]
        display('here', [idx for idx in df_.index if df_.loc[idx,'selected_rate'] > 0]) ###
        color, subset_row = 'yellow', [idx for idx in df_.index if (df_.loc[idx,'selected_rate']>top_useless)]
        if group == 'Always': ## 위 동점기준 필요 ##
            color, subset_row = 'red', pool[0]
            features, num_features = [pool[0]], 1
        elif group == 'Useful':
            features, num_features = pool, len(pool)
        elif group == 'Normal':
            features, num_features = pool+[None], len(pool)+1
        else :
            features, num_features = [], 0
        display(df_.style.set_caption('Pool{} Group : {}'.format(i_, group)).\
                applymap(lambda x : 'background-color : '+color, subset=(subset_row, slice(None))))
        result.append([num_features, features]) 
    df_result[['num_features', 'features']] = np.array(result,dtype=object)
    display(df_result)    

    # 경우의 수 # 
    num_cases = np.prod(df_result[df_result['group'].isin(['Useful', 'Normal'])]['num_features'].values)
    print('\n\n\n\n ### 총 경우의 수 : {} ###'.format(num_cases))
    ## 컬럼 수 설정 ## ## 여러 케이스들이 나올 수 있도록 모델단에서 이루어져야 함
    if num_col <= num_Always :
        df_result = df_result.iloc[:num_col]
    elif num_col <= num_Always+num_Useful :
        df_ = df_result[df_result['group']=='Useful']
        df_ = df_.sample(frac=1).iloc[:num_col-(num_Always)]
        df_result = pd.concat([df_result[df_result['group']=='Always'], df_])
    elif num_col <= num_Always+num_Useful+num_Normal :
        df_ = df_result[df_result['group']=='Normal']
        df_ = df_.sample(frac=1).iloc[:num_col-(num_Always+num_Useful)]
        df_result = pd.concat([df_result[df_result['group'].isin(['Always','Useful'])], df_])
    else :
        pass
    df_result = df_result.sort_values(['top_selected_rate', 'top_rank_sum'], ascending=[False, True])
    num_cases = np.prod(df_result[df_result['group'].isin(['Useful', 'Normal'])]['num_features'].values)
    print('\n 설정한 컬럼 개수 : {} \n 조정된 경우의 수 : {}'.format(num_col, num_cases))
    display(df_result)
    ## 경우의 수 설정 ##
    cases_change = False
    while num_cases > cases :
        cases_change = True
        df_result = df_result[:-1]
        num_cases = np.prod(df_result[df_result['group'].isin(['Useful', 'Normal'])]['num_features'].values)
    if cases_change:
        print('\n 설정한 경우의 수 한도 : {} \n 조정된 경우의 수 : {}'.format(cases, num_cases))
        display(df_result)
    
    # 최종 pool 결과
    print('\n\n\n\n ### Pool 간 선별 결과 ###')
    for i, r in zip(df_result.sort_index().index, df_result.sort_index()['features']):
        print('Pool{} : \n {} \n'.format(i,r))
    return list(df_result.sort_index()['features'].values)

result = selection_inter_pool(pools_, data, 'body_mass_g', 'reg', n=0.5, num_col=10, cases=100)
```

```python
# https://stackoverflow.com/questions/62537457/right-way-to-use-rfecv-and-permutation-importance-sklearn 
# 기준을 Feature Importance 대신 Permutation Importance로 바꾸는 법     
# RFE
# -> 모델 
from sklearn.feature_selection import RFE, RFECV

#     3. 반복적 특성 선택
#     마지막으로 RFE (recursive feature elimination)는 Backward 방식중 하나로, 
#     모든 변수를 우선 다 포함시킨 후 반복해서 학습을 진행하면서 중요도가 낮은 변수를 하나씩 제거하는 방식이다.

#     일변량 분석 -> 모델 사용 x 
#     모델기반 선택 -> 하나의 모델 사용해 특성 선택
#     반복적 특성 선택 -> 특성의 수가 각기 다른 일련의 모델
#     기본적으로 2가지 방법 
#     1. 특성을 하나도 선택하지 않은 상태로 시작해 -> 어떤 종료 조건을 도달 할때까지 하나씩 추가하는 방법
#     2. 모든 특성을 가지고 시작해 -> 어떤 종료 조건이 될 때까지 하나씩 추가하는 방법
#     모델이 만들어지기 때문에 -> 계산 비용이 훨씬 많이 듬
#     재귀적 특성 제거가 이런 방법의 하나
#     이 방법은 모든 특성으로 시작해 모델 만들고 가장 낮은 특성부터 제거 
#     -> 그런 다음 제거한 특성 빼고 나머지 특성 전체로 새로운 모델 -> 미리 정의한 특성개수 남을 때 까지 계속
#     -> 특성의 중요도를 결정하는 방법 제공

#  RFE(Recursive Feature Elimination)는 어떤 관점에서 바라 보면 feature selection의 가장 단순한 방법이다. 모든 feature들로부터 feature를 하나하나 제거하면서 원하는 개수의 feature가 남을 때까지 이를 반복한다. 즉, 학습하고 싶은 모델을 정하고, 이 모델로 모든 feature를 활용하여 데이터를 학습했을 때(full model)의 각 feature의 feature importance를 도출한다. 그리고 feature importance가 낮은 feature부터 하나씩 제거해가면서 원하는 feature 개수가 될 때까지 이를 반복하는 것이다. 이렇게 원하는 feature 개수에 해당하는 상위 feature importance를 가지는 feature들이 최종 feature selection 결과가 된다.

# RFECV
#  RFE를 사용할 때에 가장 큰 단점은 몇 개의 feature를 남겨야 할 지를 사용자가 직접 정의해야 한다는 점이다. 이러한 단점을 극복하기 위해 등장한 것이 RFECV이다. RFECV(Recursive Feature Elimination with Cross Validation)는 위의 RFE가 사용하던 방법과 똑같이 가장 feature importance가 낮은 feature들을 제거해가면서 각 feature 개수마다 모델의 성능을 계산한다. 이 때, 각 feature 개수마다 K-fole validation 등의 cross validation을 활용하여 각기 다른 성능을 도출한다. 

# RFECV의 score 결과. 가장 높은 결과를 가지는 feature 개수가 3이다.
#  이렇게 도출된 각 feature 개수별 성능을 평균내어 가장 높은 성능을 가지는 feature 개수에 해당하는 feature들을 최종 feature selection 결과로 사용한다.

select = RFE(RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=10, random_state=42),
             n_features_to_select=2) # 40번 실행

select.fit(X_train_clf, y_train_clf)

cols = iris.feature_names
mask = select.get_support() # 선택된 특성 boolen 값
plt.matshow(mask.reshape(1, -1), fignum=10, cmap='Blues')
plt.xticks(range(len(cols)), cols, rotation=90)
plt.xlabel('features')
plt.yticks([0]);


# 어떤 입력값 넣을지 확신 X -> 특성 자동 선택이 도움이 된다.
# ->예측 속도를 높이거나 해석하기 더 쉬운 모델을 만드는데 필요한 만큼 특성의 수를 줄이는데 효과적
# _> 대부분 실전에서는 큰 향상 끌어내진 못한다.
# 그래도 특정 선택은 중요한 도구이다.
# # 반복적 선택 방법 1.전진 선택법 2. 후진 선택법 3. 교차 선택법 scikit-learn 제공 x
# 하지면 회귀 모델 score R^2 값을 어들 수 잇으므로 직접 구현 할 수있다.
# 전진 선택법 -> 하나씩 교대로 포함 -> 가장 높은 R^2 특성 추가해 나가고
# 후진 선택법은 -> 하나씩 빼면서 가장 낮은 R^2 되는 특성 제거하면 된다.
```

```python
    print('selected_features :', '\n', list(selected), len(list(selected))) 

    cols = X.columns
    mask = select.get_support() # 선택된 특성 boolen 값. 선택되면 True(0) # select.support_ : model_selection에만 존재
    plt.matshow(mask.reshape(1, -1), cmap='Blues', fignum=0, vmin=0, vmax=1) 
    # vmin,vmax 부재 시 T,F 중 다수인 쪽이 진한 색이 되어 일관성 없음. 
    plt.xticks(range(len(cols)), cols, rotation=30)
    plt.yticks([])
    plt.xlabel('Features')
    plt.ylabel('Selected')
    plt.show()
    
        
def plot_cv(method) : # Plot number of features VS. cross-validation scores
    global select
    select = method
    num_of_feature_range = range(select.min_features_to_select, len(cols)+1, 1)
    print(select.grid_scores_)
    plt.figure(figsize=(16,2))
    plt.plot(num_of_feature_range, select.grid_scores_); 
    plt.xlabel("Number of features selected")
    plt.ylabel("Cross validation score (accuracy)")
    plt.xticks(list(num_of_feature_range))
    plt.show()

    display(select.cv_results_)
    plt.figure(figsize=(16,2))
    plt.plot(num_of_feature_range, select.cv_results_['mean_test_score'])
    plt.xlabel("Number of features selected")
    plt.ylabel("Cross validation score (accuracy)")
    plt.xticks(list(num_of_feature_range))
    plt.show() 
   
    
def feature_selection_all(data, target, task,
                          method1 = VarianceThreshold(threshold=0.001),
                          method2 = SelectPercentile(percentile=50), # SelectKBest(k=2)       
                          method3 = RFECV(estimator=DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), cv=3, scoring='accuracy', n_jobs=-1),
                          method4 = SelectFromModel(estimator=DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), threshold='1.25*mean')
                          ):
    
    global X, y, cols, select, lst_select
    X,y = data.drop([target], axis=1), data[target]
    cols = X.columns
    lst_select = []
    
    # VarianceThreshold
    print('# Variance method')
    feature_selection(method1)
    print('Variance :', '\n', select.variances_)
          
    # Univariate feature selection. 일변량 방법 # SelectPercentile, SelectKBest
    print('\n\n\n # F-test method')
    if task == 'reg':
        arg = f_regression # mutual_info_classif
    else :
        arg = f_classif # mutual_info_regression, chi2   
    param = method2.get_params(deep=False) 
    param['score_func'] = arg # param 변경 # param = {**method2.get_params(deep=False), **{'estimator':model}} 
    method2 = SelectPercentile(**param)  
    feature_selection(method2)
    print('p_val :', '\n',  select.pvalues_)
    print('f_stats :', '\n',  select.scores_)   

    
    ## Model Based (Wrapper, Embedded) ##
    models = [DecisionTreeClassifier(random_state=1), 
              RandomForestClassifier(random_state=1), 
              GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=1), 
              LGBMClassifier(random_state=1), 
              XGBClassifier(random_state=1)]
   
    # RFE
    print('\n\n\n # RFECV method')
    for model in models :
        print('Model :', model)
        param = method3.get_params(deep=False) 
        param['estimator'] = model
        param['min_features_to_select'] = 1 # int(len(cols)*0.3)
        method3 = RFECV(**param) 
        feature_selection(method3)
        print("Feature Ranking: %s" % select.ranking_)
        plot_cv(select)
        print()

    # Selection Using Model
    print('\n\n\n  # Model Selection method')
    for model in models :
        print('Model :', model)
        param = method4.get_params(deep=False) 
        param['estimator'] = model
        method4 = SelectFromModel(**param)  
        feature_selection(method4)

    # final_selection 
    print('\n\n\n # Final Selection')
    num_method = 12
    df_voting = pd.Series(np.hstack(lst_select)).value_counts()
    display(df_voting) 
    display(df_voting/num_method*100)
    print('selected features from 90% of methods  : ', '\n', df_voting [df_voting >= num_method*0.9].index.tolist())
    
    return df_voting.index.tolist()[:1] # 수정가능 : voting top1 + voting rate over 90%
```

```python
from sklearn.feature_selection import SelectFromModel
# SelectFromModel은 (지도 학습 모델로 계산된) 중요도가 지정한 임게치보다 큰 모든 특성 선택
```

```python
data = pd.read_csv('./df_penguin_processed_221115-Copy1.csv', encoding='cp949')
data.head(2)

for i,j in product(pool1,pool2) :
    p1 = [i] 
    p2 = [j]
    x = data[p1+p2]
    y = data['body_mass_g']
    
    model_ = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=1) # SelectFromModel 내에 F.E 제공하는 attribute가 없어 대체
    model_.fit(x, y) 
    print(i,'/',j,'\n',model_.feature_importances_)
    
print('\n')
for i in pool1 :
    p1 = [i]
    p2 = pool2
    x = data[p1+p2]
    y = data['body_mass_g']
    
    model_ = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=1) # SelectFromModel 내에 F.E 제공하는 attribute가 없어 대체
    model_.fit(x, y) 
    print(i,'/','all_pool2','\n',model_.feature_importances_[0], model_.feature_importances_[1:].sum())

print('\n')
for j in pool2 :
    p1 = pool2
    p2 = [j]
    x = data[p1+p2]
    y = data['body_mass_g']
    
    model_ = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=1) # SelectFromModel 내에 F.E 제공하는 attribute가 없어 대체
    model_.fit(x, y) 
    print('all_pool1','/',j,'\n',model_.feature_importances_[:-1].sum(), model_.feature_importances_[-1])
```

동일 pool의 변수는 모두 상호 상관
pools = [1,2,3,4] , [4,5,6] , [6,7], [8]

장점 :
pool의 견고함 확보. ((1-2) (2-3) (3-4) 노드 연결만으로 pool이 구성되는 등의 상황 없음)  

문제점 : 중복 발생 
1) 최종변수 선택에 영향 ((4가 각 pool에서 살아남았다면..) 4는 pool별로 들어가 선택될 확률이 상승, 그 만큼 타 변수가 선택될 확률 저하)  
   <- 4가 여러 pool에 낄 정도로 영향이 높다면 선택될 확률이 높은 것도 합리적일 수 있음  
2) pool의 그룹 선정시 영향 (메기 효과 : 4가 매우 뛰어나서 4가 포함된 pool들이 모두 always. 등..)    
   <- always는 분석가 개입(도메인, 초기 try로 확인)을 통해 주로 판단하고   
   usefull, normal, useless 분류에 주안??. always가 많아지는것이 usefull이 많은것보다 많이 risky..  

대안 :   
1) 최종 선택에서 set으로 중복 처리 ->   
   1)4가 선택될 확률이 상승하고, 타 변수가 선택될 확률이 저하되는 것을 통제하지는 못함. 2) 마찬가지  
2) [1,2,3,4] [4,5,6] 에서 123이 뽑히면 456pool유지, 4가 뽑히면 56pool로 변경..  
   1) 해결? 2) X  
3) 보수적 pooling 으로 놓치는 부분들은 corr 외 방법으로 보안.. (식솔끼리 묶어주기, + 분석가 판단...)

```python
from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline, make_pipeline
from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV
from sklearn.svm import SVC, SVR
from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier


pipe = Pipeline([('classifier', LGBMClassifier())], verbose=True)

param_grid = [{'classifier': [SVC()], 
              'classifier__gamma': [0.01, 0.1, 1, 10, 100], 
              'classifier__C': [0.01, 0.1, 1, 10, 100]
              },

               {'classifier': [LogisticRegression(solver='saga', l1_ratio=0, max_iter=5000)],
               'classifier__penalty': ['l1', 'l2', 'elasticnet'], 
               'classifier__C': [0.001, 0.01, 0.1, 1, 10, 100],
               },

              {'classifier': [RandomForestClassifier()],
              'classifier__max_depth': [4, 6], # max_depth: The maximum depth of the tree.
              'classifier__n_estimators': [50, 100], # n_estimators: The number of trees in the forest.
              'classifier__min_samples_split': [50, 100]
              }] # min_samples_split: The minimum number of samples required to split an internal node       

grid = GridSearchCV(pipe, param_grid, scoring = 'accuracy', cv=5, error_score='raise')  
grid.fit(X_train, y_train)

print(grid.best_params_)
print(grid.best_score_)
```

```python
def model_pipeline_regressor(Model, Categorical_features, Numerical_features, **kwargs):

    cf_transformer = OneHotEncoder()
    nf_transformer = StandardScaler()
    
    preprocessor = ColumnTransformer([('categorical_features', cf_transformer, Categorical_features),
                                 ('numerical_features', nf_transformer, Numerical_features)])

    if Model == 'dt':
        estimator = ('ml', DecisionTreeRegressor(**kwargs))
    elif Model == 'rf':
        estimator = ('ml', RandomForestRegressor(**kwargs))
    elif Model == 'gbm':
        estimator = ('ml', GradientBoostingRegressor(**kwargs))
    elif Model == 'xgb':
        estimator = ('ml', XGBRegressor(**kwargs))
    elif Model == 'lgbm':
        estimator = ('ml', LGBMRegressor(**kwargs))
    
    pipe = Pipeline(steps=[('preprocessor', preprocessor), estimator])
    
    return pipe
```

```python
def hyper_parameter_tune_regressor(*args, n_iter, metric):
    '''
    ***************************************************************************************************************
    ***************************************************************************************************************
    - AutoML : 하이퍼 파라미터 튜닝
    : 데이터 프레임의 기본적인 통계 요약 정보 확인
    
    - Arguments
      args : 모델 별 Hyper Parameter Search 방법
            → 'grid_dt', 'random_dt', 'bayes_dt', 'grid_rf', 'random_rf', 'bayes_rf', 'grid_gbm', 'random_gbm', 
               'bayes_gbm', 'grid_xgb', 'random_xgb', 'bayes_xgb', 'grid_lgbm', 'random_lgbm', 'bayes_lgbm'
      n_iter : Search 횟수
      metric : 평가 방식 (R2, RMSE ..)
      
    - Return :
      모델 별 Search에 따른 Model Performance, Best Model
    
    - Usage : 
      hyper_parameter_tune_regressor('random_dt', 'random_rf', n_iter = 3, metric = r2_score)
    ***************************************************************************************************************
    ***************************************************************************************************************
    '''
    # Final Edit : `22.10.21  / # Authors: Byeongjun
    
    scoring = 'r2'
    
    temp = []
    temp.extend(args)

    %run -i '/jupyter_home/user02/Untitled Folder/Hyper_Parameter.py'
       
    model_candidate = []
    model_name = []
    for i in temp:
        model_candidate.append(model_dict[i][0])
        model_name.append(model_dict[i][1])

    model_name *= n_iter
    print('Model Performance ...\n')
    model_performance = []
    x = 0
    for _ in range(n_iter):
        for i, model in enumerate(model_candidate):
            x += 1
            print('\niteration :', x)
            KST = datetime.now(timezone('Asia/Seoul'))  # Korea Standard Time
            print('------------------------------------------------------------------------------------')
            print('- Algorithm: ', model_name[i], '....................', KST.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'))
            start_time = time.time()
            model.fit(X_train, y_train)
            print('- Best Accuracy: {0:.4f}'.format(model.best_score_))
            print('- Best Hyper Parameter: ', model.best_params_)
            print('- Train Accuracy: {0:.4f}'.format(metric(y_train, model.predict(X_train))))
            print('- Test Accuracy: {0:.4f}'.format(metric(y_test, model.predict(X_test))))
            print("- Learning Time: {0:.1f} sec ".format(time.time() - start_time), '\n')
            model_performance.append(metric(y_test, model.predict(X_test)))
            
    print('- Best Model: ', model_name[model_performance.index(max(model_performance))], 
          '(iter #',model_performance.index(max(model_performance)) + 1,')')
    print('- Best Accuracy: {0:.4f}'.format(max(model_performance)))
```
